text:
My go-to fix would be to set the ul to display:flex (gotta use flex on everything), but you can also just remove the float on the child li elements.

What ever you do, either nix or adjust the min-width to keep it from being so wide :-)
```.hs-menu-wrapper.hs-menu-flow-horizontal.flyouts &gt; ul li.hs-item-has-children ul.hs-menu-children-wrapper {
...
    display: flex;
    min-width: unset;
    flex-flow: column;
}```
